{"tid":1718180,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「正視聽」 癱瘓獨裁政權社會運作乃爭取民主手段","createTime":"2019-11-13T19:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T10:36:27.000Z","uid":119607,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30e183b124d71968f11ef1e9b214dca25b0e9d4d","tid":1718180,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:18:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港非民主社會，政府不是民選，唔能夠用民主國家嘅社會運動嚟批評香港示威者影響民生。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家見到啲曱甴外媒仲問堵塞道路就係你地嘅民主時候，答番佢係爭取民主手段。<br />\n<br />\nPs火魔地舖我不太支持，如果上面有手足住咁點。<br />\n好多外媒都唔指出香港唔係民主社會，係根本上嘅錯誤理解。"},{"pid":"953cb7e2017580c4f25abee4c5413132a6a92e8d","tid":1718180,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:23:48.000Z","msg":"推比多啲人睇，唔洗口啞啞。"},{"pid":"109de1b7279311baf4619c4d797d02e8d70da113","tid":1718180,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:32:57.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"ab391eb8cd8128293f06df81b6988b7d20f7cabc","tid":1718180,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:37:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"869522fd2fb892d07bef17cbd3a0e91bc5bd2713","tid":1718180,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:42:50.000Z","msg":"結束政府，親共外媒，華媒謊言。"},{"pid":"c00daa1b6455cd24d9dc321ed72401b5efb5eb85","tid":1718180,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:44:40.000Z","msg":"自古人民爭取權力，都是癱瘓社會運作。<br />\n民主是吸納反對聲音，讓社會回歸和平。<br />\n依家唔民主，點和平？"},{"pid":"a3ee449e60119496899a769f9d7d83b092b74d2a","tid":1718180,"uid":276783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:45:19.000Z","msg":"求下各位文宣手足幫手搵資料<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1718140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1718140</a><br />\n<br />\n求幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9a7cd402f41694b4d9ef1cceb015c7160efc8c","tid":1718180,